text: No beauty shines brighter than that of a good heart.
Tough times never last, but tough people do
You were given this life because you are strong enough to live it.
Love is in the air so just breath and care.
Diabetes is unique not a critique.
Life is not over because you have diabetes. Make the most of what you have, be grateful.
If there is no struggle, there is no progress.
You may have diabetes, but diabetes does not have you.
Motivation is what gets you started, habit is what keeps you going.
Managing your diabetes is not a science, it is an art.
